Classes in org.promasi.core.equations that implement IEquation
 class CalculatedEquation
          The calculated equation takes a string that represents the equation for example : x*y where x and y are the keys of the ISdObject that exist as a dependency in the CalculatedEquation._context.
 class ConstantEquation
          The constant equation returns always the value that was used to initialize the equation.
 class ExternalEquation
          The external equation takes its value from the upper layer using the Communicator.
 class LookupEquation
          The LookupEquation is used to create user specific graphs.
